| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0726 — Recovery Inhibition (everest)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a5b4812a-e9f5-50eb-8f64-cd3aad5bdcfc"
